Deprecated Classes
foxtrot.pumps.SunJDK140ConditionalEventPump
          This class implements a workaround for bug #4531693 that has been fixed in JDK 1.4.2 and backported to 1.4.1. Therefore it is recommended to upgrade to those fixed JDK versions, as the bug not only affects Foxtrot but also the usage of dialogs.
